{"tid":2511071,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【ViuTV】《無限斜棟有限公司》 大結局(39)","createTime":"2021-04-30T15:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T15:24:20.000Z","uid":53673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71a9e8d93ef28a4aadaf706e3f1ebabd5bbe36b3","tid":2511071,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uJIYglufHik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuJIYglufHik&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqROoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=15d88ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uJIYglufHik</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n陳家晞（盧慧敏 飾）的父親陳鎮東本是「全知偵探社」老闆。這家公司其後經易手，並由張諾恆（陳卓賢 飾）奪得一切權利。李展翹（黃定謙飾）隨後加入公司。陳家晞、張諾恆及李展翹後來更改偵探社的定位，由純粹為客人蒐證的偵探社改為「無限斜棟有限公司」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《無限斜棟有限公司》將於2021年4月5日起，逢星期一至五21:30-22:30於ViuTV播放</strong></p></blockquote>"},{"pid":"81acb4c6fbd780db65b97bb7629f2cbba06e72a4","tid":2511071,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"妖治ching收咗工，所以我開住先"},{"pid":"c2b0c99feca87bd8a34b51d58b299427bccce5e9","tid":2511071,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"三爺成長史<br />\n<br />\n本來係香港沙灘排球嘅明日之星<br />\n但因為參加咗全民造星之後整斷手<br />\n受傷退役轉咗去力圖打港排<br />\n成功做埋港隊 但可惜魯蛇關係被逼收手<br />\n終日沉迷網絡 自己channel有10k followers<br />\n因為一次同個地產佬靈探事件<br />\n網上識咗個碗碗 之後仲日久生情<br />\n但係俾方蛇破壞<br />\n最終三爺成為咗痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推到三爺手抄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做下輯主角復仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e2829755c35cc95f87932386b994ecc5db936b","tid":2511071,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-